      "item": {
        "type": "html",
        "id": "068f033287a57b1f",
        "text": "Amici del Nidiaci in Oltrarno, an English-language website, provides a listing of specific activities and practices at the Nidiaci Community Garden. [http://www.nidiaci.com/category/english/ html]\n"
